# ── Facebook Graph API ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Required for the live Facebook feed on the website.
#
# How to get these:
#  1. Go to https://developers.facebook.com and create an App (type: Business)
#  2. Add "Facebook Login for Business" product
#  3. Generate a User Access Token with pages_read_engagement permission
#  4. Exchange it for a long-lived Page Access Token via Graph API Explorer
#  5. Copy your numeric Page ID from the page's About section or Graph API
#
# Never commit the real .env file — keep this .env.example in git instead.

VITE_FB_PAGE_ID=your_numeric_page_id_here
VITE_FB_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_long_lived_page_access_token_here
